## Curation Stages

| Stage | Purpose | Method | Config |
|-------|---------|--------|--------|
| Exact Dedup | Remove identical conversations | SHA-256 content hash | deduplicate.exact_match |
| Semantic Dedup | Remove near-duplicates | Sentence embeddings + cosine similarity | deduplicate.semantic_threshold |
| PII Redaction | Remove personal info | Microsoft Presidio | pii_redact.enabled |
| Quality Filter | Remove low-quality data | Heuristics (length, ratio, etc.) | quality.enabled |

## Configuration

```text
curate:
  deduplicate:
    enabled: true
    exact_match: true
    semantic_threshold: 0.95
  pii_redact:
    enabled: true
    entities:
      - PERSON
      - EMAIL_ADDRESS
      - PHONE_NUMBER
      - LOCATION
      - CREDIT_CARD
      - CRYPTO_WALLET
      - IP_ADDRESS
      - URL
    custom_patterns: []
  quality:
    enabled: true
    min_messages: 2
    max_tokens: 8192
    min_user_ratio: 0.1
    max_user_ratio: 0.9
    min_avg_message_len: 10
```

## Exact Deduplication

Computes SHA-256 hash of normalized conversation content. Removes exact duplicates (same messages, same order). Fast: O(n) with hash set lookup. Typical removal: 3-8% of conversations.

## Semantic Deduplication

Uses sentence-transformers/all-MiniLM-L6-v2 embeddings. Computes cosine similarity between conversation embeddings. Pairs above threshold (default 0.95) marked as duplicates. Keeps first occurrence, removes subsequent. Typical removal: 2-5% additional.

```text
embeddings = model.encode(conversations)
similarities = cosine_similarity(embeddings)
duplicates = find_pairs(similarities > threshold)
```

## PII Redaction (Presidio)

| Entity | Example | Action |
|--------|---------|--------|
| PERSON | John Smith | Replace with [PERSON] |
| EMAIL_ADDRESS | john@example.com | Replace with [EMAIL] |
| PHONE_NUMBER | +1-555-123-4567 | Replace with [PHONE] |
| LOCATION | San Francisco | Replace with [LOCATION] |
| CREDIT_CARD | 4242 4242 4242 4242 | Replace with [CREDIT_CARD] |
| CRYPTO_WALLET | 0x742d35Cc... | Replace with [WALLET] |

Custom patterns via pii_redact.custom_patterns.

## Quality Filters

| Filter | Description | Default |
|--------|-------------|---------|
| min_messages | Minimum conversation turns | 2 |
| max_tokens | Maximum tokens (estimated) | 8192 |
| min_user_ratio | User/(User+Assistant) minimum | 0.1 |
| max_user_ratio | User/(User+Assistant) maximum | 0.9 |
| min_avg_message_len | Average chars per message | 10 |

## Running Curation

### Standalone

```bash
hermetic curate ./hermetic-output --dedup-exact --dedup-semantic --pii-redact --quality-filter -o ./curated
```

### During Import

```bash
hermetic import ~/exports/chatgpt.json --curate -o ./output
```

