## CLI Reference

```bash
hermetic curate [OPTIONS] INPUT_PATH

Options:
  -o, --output PATH           Output directory
  -f, --format FORMAT         Output format
  --dedup-exact/--no-dedup-exact
  --dedup-semantic/--no-dedup-semantic
  --semantic-threshold FLOAT  Default: 0.95
  --pii-redact/--no-pii-redact
  --quality-filter/--no-quality-filter
  -c, --config PATH           Config file
```
